        "content": "<p>Oh, no, it's meant to be \"there is a least f satisfying (i), and this least f also satisfies (ii)\", not \"there is a least f satisfying both (i) and (ii)\".<br>\nsarahzrf pointed out earlier that I'd been unclear in that regard, but I didn't edit the post to clarify it then. I'll do that now.</p>",
